{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2e7ca684ef","title":"如敌决心开战红军主力可分三步出击","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"550d2227cc","index":0,"year":1937,"month":1,"day":8,"articleId":"2e7ca684ef"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji10","name":"毛泽东全集第10卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji10.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji10":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5f8d113eeb","type":"paragraph","text":"如敌决心开战红军主力可分三步出击","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"2e7ca684ef"},{"id":"b0936a9fea","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年1月8日）彭、任”甲、到三原后，准备体息三天，情况许可，再延长至五天或七大，请规定工作日程。十五军团在威阳亦然乙、如敌决心开战，红军主力应以第一步出商洛网，第二步出像西，第三步出京汉路为上策。如此方能改变整个局势，分化南京，迫蒋就范。留二方面军在消北策应友军在内线作战。尔后内线之红军与友军同外线之红军主力互相策应为战路上之配合作战但目前争取在三原、咸阳多休息几天，不致和平被敌人破坏，一时不向东出动。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"2e7ca684ef"},{"id":"800a81ff90","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"2e7ca684ef"},{"id":"bae556dc7e","type":"paragraph","text":"八日三十四时委员。[1]彭、任，指彭德怀、任弱时，当时分别任红军前敌总指挥和政治21商洛，指陕西商州和洛南。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"2e7ca684ef"}],"page":{"id":"e48c34bac1","publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"2e7ca684ef","start":129,"end":129}}}},"__N_SSG":true}